==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Profiling
<hw>Pro"fil*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Fort.)</fld> <def>In the
construction of fieldworks, the erection at proper intervals of wooden
profiles, to show to the workmen the sectional form of the parapets at
those points.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Profilist</ent>⟦br⟧
